# The Method in which scrap the data from the websites(like flipkart,amazon etc) are called web scrapping.
# Web scraping is likely to used in big MNC's where they need to generate data from various web portal and after that compare it.

# There are three areas where Web Scraping is used to get data.
# 1. Data Science - we can use web scrapping in order to generate data then the data scientist will do research on it.
# 2. Machine Learning - we can used web scrapping in order to generate data so that machine learning algorithm would made.
# 3. Automation - we can used web scrapping in order to generate data so that automation engineer can have vision it and try it for creating various automations.